players.name: Lawrence Mulenga
players.summary: Tresford Lawrence Mulenga is a Zambian professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Power Dynamos and the Zambia national team.

players.name: Frankie Musonda
players.summary: Frankie Chisenga Musonda is a professional footballer who plays as a defender. Born in England, he plays for the Zambia national team.

players.name: Lubambo Musonda
players.summary: Lubambo Musonda is a Zambian professional footballer who plays as a left winger for German 2. Bundesliga club 1. FC Magdeburg and the Zambia national team.

players.name: Stoppila Sunzu
players.summary: Stoppila Sunzu, also known as Stophira Sunzu, is a Zambian professional footballer who plays as a centre-back for Chinese Super League club Changchun Yatai. He scored the winning penalty kick for Zambia in the 2012 Africa Cup of Nations final.

players.name: Kabaso Chongo
players.summary: Kabaso Chongo is a Zambian professional footballer who plays as a defender for Linafoot club TP Mazembe.

players.name: Dominic Chanda
players.summary: Dominic Chanda is a Zambian professional footballer who plays as a defender for Kabwe Warriors and the Zambia national football team.

players.name: David Hamansenya
players.summary: David Hamansenya is a Zambian professional footballer who plays as a left-back for the Segunda División club Leganés and the Zambia national team.

players.name: Gift Mphande
players.summary: Gift Prosper Mphande is a Zambian professional footballer who plays as a centre-back for Zambian club ZESCO United and the Zambia national team.

players.name: Miguel Chaiwa
players.summary: Miguel Changa Chaiwa is a Zambian professional footballer who plays as a defensive midfielder for Scottish Premiership club Hibernian and the Zambia national team.

players.name: Benson Sakala
players.summary: Benson Sakala is a Zambian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Bohemians 1905 and the Zambia national team where he has been appointed captain ahead of 2023 AFCON qualifiers.

players.name: Kings Kangwa
players.summary: Kings Kangwa is a Zambian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Israeli Premier League club Hapoel Be'er Sheva and the Zambia national team.

players.name: Joseph Liteta
players.summary: Joseph Liteta is a Zambian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Cagliari Primavera U20 team of Italian team Cagliari.

players.name: Jack Lahne
players.summary: Jack Daniel Kalichi Lahne is a professional footballer who plays as striker for 2. Liga club Austria Lustenau. A former youth international for Sweden, he plays for the Zambia national team.

players.name: Lameck Banda
players.summary: Lameck Banda is a Zambian professional footballer who plays as a left winger for Serie A club Lecce and the Zambia national team.

players.name: Fashion Sakala
players.summary: Junior Fashion Sakala is a Zambian professional footballer who plays as a forward for Saudi Pro League club Al-Fayha and the Zambia national team.

players.name: Kennedy Musonda
players.summary: Kennedy Musonda is a Zambian professional footballer who plays as a striker for Liga Leumit club Hapoel Ramat Gan and the Zambia national team.

players.name: Patson Daka
players.summary: Patson Daka is a Zambian professional footballer who plays as a striker for EFL Championship club Leicester City and the Zambia national team.
